title: Football is BACK! Training camp talk with Jason La Canfora (Football 8/1)
description:
Will Brinson and Jason La Canfora break down the latest news and notes from around the NFL, including the Michael Thomas signing (2:00), other holdouts around the league (8:00), Andrew Luck's injury (15:00), Carson Wentz and Eagles expectations (20:00) plus what else JLC is hearing around training camps.
